Time":"2017-08-30T16:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朝早 落M記食早餐睇報紙<br />\n之後去睇早場戲<br />\n<br />\n晏晝 去就保齡球場 碌拎<br />\n<br />\n碌完去食下午茶（skip lunch）<br />\n<br />\n食完就行返屋企，沿途睇下周圍嘅人同事<br />\n<br />\n順便買個飯盒/返到屋企就等屋企人煮飯<br />\n<br />\n之後大教訓。</blockquote><br />\n呢個睇落唔錯<br />\n好似幾啱毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我未試過一個人去碌拎<br />\n自己一個去碌會唔會好怪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d876d7779066d49dc29e9e9f30e4732e431e683c","tid":381143,"uid":23115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>模型<br />\npuzzle<br />\n煮野食<br />\n飲酒<br />\n沖咖啡<br />\n睇戲<br />\n開車兜風<br />\n釣魚<br />\n睇戲睇書<br />\n練字<br />\n行山<br />\n<br />\n大把wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打同你一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實毒撚一個更開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n單身個排啲時間真係好好用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}